<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<Defs>

    <TraitDef>
		<defName>AK_Trait_Agent_SRT</defName>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>SRT学院学生</label>
				<description>{PAWN_nameDef}是SRT学院的学生。</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<MoveSpeed>1.0</MoveSpeed>
					<HuntingStealth>0.5</HuntingStealth>
				</statOffsets>
				<skillGains>
					<Shooting>4</Shooting>
				</skillGains>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
	</TraitDef>

    <TraitDef>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<defName>AK_Trait_Miyako</defName>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>无表情系</label>
				<description>宫子平常总是没什么表情，看上去甚至有些木讷，但是实际上内心是个很善良很富有正义感的孩子，也很关心自己的队友们。</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<SocialImpact>-0.05</SocialImpact>
					<PsychicSensitivity>0.2</PsychicSensitivity>
				</statOffsets>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
	</TraitDef>

    <TraitDef>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<defName>AK_Trait_MiyakoSecond</defName>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>小动物爱好者</label>
				<description>宫子很喜欢小动物，尤其是小兔子，一但在街上看到可爱的小动物就很容易走不动道了。</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<TameAnimalChance>1.0</TameAnimalChance>
					<TrainAnimalChance>0.5</TrainAnimalChance>
				</statOffsets>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
	</TraitDef>

    <TraitDef>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<defName>AK_Trait_Saki</defName>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>过分严谨</label>
				<description>咲是一个很严谨，做事很认真的孩子，但是因为太过盲信教科书上的内容而不懂变通，经常会做出某些不必要的繁琐行为，甚至因此闹出笑话。</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<SocialImpact>-0.1</SocialImpact>
					<WorkSpeedGlobal>0.15</WorkSpeedGlobal>
                    <GlobalLearningFactor>0.2</GlobalLearningFactor>
                    <AimingDelayFactor>-0.2</AimingDelayFactor>
                    <ShootingAccuracyPawn>0.15</ShootingAccuracyPawn>
					<ResearchSpeed>0.8</ResearchSpeed>
				</statOffsets>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
	</TraitDef>

    <TraitDef>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<defName>AK_Trait_SakiSecond</defName>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>严格训练</label>
				<description>咲对于规矩有着很严格的追求，对自己时刻保持着一定的管束并遵守军纪</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<RestRateMultiplier>0.15</RestRateMultiplier>
				</statOffsets>
                <disallowedMentalStates>
                    <li>InsultingSpree</li>
                    <li>TargetedInsultingSpree</li>
                </disallowedMentalStates>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
	</TraitDef>

    <TraitDef>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<defName>AK_Trait_Moe</defName>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>破坏发烧友</label>
				<description>萌绘不知道为什么，对于毁坏事务上情有独钟，尤其是把各种完好的东西毁的一干二净，她最喜欢的就是用爆破物炸毁东西。\n如果你认识萌绘的话一定要管理好电脑，除非你希望你电脑上所有资料都被删干净。</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<MentalBreakThreshold>0.1</MentalBreakThreshold>
				</statOffsets>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
	</TraitDef>

    <TraitDef>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<defName>AK_Trait_MoeSecond</defName>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>靠谱的后勤员</label>
				<description>排除掉喜欢搞破坏这点，萌绘在后勤和编程方面的专业素质是绝对过硬的，你可以放心的把编程和数据问题交给她，不过别完全交给她，她可能不保存就关掉文件然后痴笑个不停。</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<GlobalLearningFactor>0.2</GlobalLearningFactor>
					<TradePriceImprovement>0.12</TradePriceImprovement>
                    <ResearchSpeed>0.8</ResearchSpeed>
				</statOffsets>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
	</TraitDef>

    <TraitDef>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<defName>AK_Trait_Miyu</defName>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>极度自卑</label>
				<description>因为存在感弱很少与人交流，美游开始惧怕与人交流，终日沉迷于消极妄想和逃避现实。但这也许是她身为狙击手的唯一骄傲。</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<SocialImpact>-0.4</SocialImpact>
                    <MentalBreakThreshold>0.08</MentalBreakThreshold>
				</statOffsets>
                <disallowedMentalStates>
                    <li>InsultingSpree</li>
                    <li>TargetedInsultingSpree</li>
                </disallowedMentalStates>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
	</TraitDef>

    <TraitDef>
		<ignoreConfigErrors>true</ignoreConfigErrors>
		<commonality>0.0</commonality>
		<defName>AK_Trait_MiyuSecond</defName>
		<degreeDatas>
			<li>
				<label>存在感很弱的狙击手</label>
				<description>过分的天赋在任务上为她带来极高的便利，加上后天不断地训练加强，她的才能早已和日常生活融合一体，作为狙击手她能够很轻易的隐藏自己，不过对于日常生活来说就不太好了。</description>
				<statOffsets>
					<MeleeDodgeChance>0.2</MeleeDodgeChance>
					<AimingDelayFactor>0.1</AimingDelayFactor>
                    <ShootingAccuracyPawn>0.35</ShootingAccuracyPawn>
				</statOffsets>
			</li>
		</degreeDatas>
	</TraitDef>

</Defs>